---
subtitle: output logs when using `outputType=json`
---

## Description

Sets whether to output Flyways standard logs in JSON format when `outputType` is set to `json`.

## Type

Boolean

## Default

`false`

## Usage

### Command-line

```powershell
./flyway info -outputType=json -outputLogsInJson=true
```

### Environment Variable

Not available

### API

Not available

### Gradle

Not available

### Maven

Not available

## Use Cases

You will require both JSON output and Flyways logs. Can be useful when diagnosing issues with Flyway's dependencies or Flyway itself.
